posting_body: ['This spacious and newly renovated 3BR house is located minutes from Hollywood Beach.', 'The property offers a HUGE back yard, plenty of parking space on the side of the house and on the street, no HOA, and convenient access to major highways.', 'Quiet and peaceful neighborhood.', 'Pets allowed except aggressive breeds.', 'THIS IS A YEARLY LEASE.', 'Landlord requires First Month and 2 Months Security Deposit to move in (3 month’s rent).', ' Landlord can work with rough credit with more money down, background check and PROOF of income showing sustained combined incomes at least 2.5-3 times the amount of the monthly rent.', 'Must have no judgments or money owed to previous landlords.', 'Dianne Warren,', 'show contact info', ', Beachfront Realty.', ' Map view is approximate, not exact, for security reasons.', 'Please CALL to view this property.', ' No texts or emails for first contact.', ' Private owner property.']
